### Variables
# The management API runs on port 40301 (mapped in docker-compose)
# Replace {{userId}} with the actual user ID you want to target

### Send hangout invite notification
POST http://localhost:40301/api/exchanges/%2F/zuyp.notifications/publish
Authorization: Basic guest guest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "properties": {},
  "routing_key": "user-01234566-8f09-4567-4af8-def000000014",
  "payload": "{\"type\":\"hangout_invite\",\"hangoutId\":\"10000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002\"}",
  "payload_encoding": "string"
}

### Send zuyp alert notification
POST http://localhost:40301/api/exchanges/%2F/zuyp.notifications/publish
Authorization: Basic guest guest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "properties": {},
  "routing_key": "user-01234566-8f09-4567-4af8-def000000014",
  "payload": "{\"type\":\"zuyp_alert\",\"hangoutId\":\"10000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002\"}",
  "payload_encoding": "string"
}
